{
  "stem": "26983.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The foreign officers said, now we don't need anymore the coverage of the Czech transport.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they went to the gas.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyhow, even if on arrival, we had to play the role only for six months.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In our Kartotek, in our own files, it was written-- six months, SB, which meant Sonderbehandlung in that language.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "After six months, they should go--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Special treatment, meaning to go to gas.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But six months, we have to--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to play this life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And therefore, the first transport who came with us were--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--were sent to gas exactly after six months, on the 7th of March '44.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there was a whole story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How it happened, I can't give you details-- it's Fredy Hirsch and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was one of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had a chance to--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--save his life-- like Korczak-- very similar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he went-- he killed-- I mean, he poisoned himself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I met him a day before, because I knew him on the children block.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He took some pills which he had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they prepared some uprising, but it didn't came to it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Only some doctors, twins, and some people who were sick at that time-- for one reason or another-- and were on the block of the sick people, survived.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the devious thing of the Germans, they knew sick people, of course they to gas.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And here you see, they leave sick people in the camp, which means you other people, surely you go to other working place-- and also distributed between the SS, to us, that we go to Heydebreck and all kinds of places-- I mean, this other transport.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we knew that soon will be an appel-- I mean, call-- and all people from the older transport had to go a different way.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
